text: Renato Cattaneo may refer to: * Renato Cattaneo (footballer, born 1903), Italian football player and coach who played for the Italian national team, Alessandria and Roma in the 1930s and later managed Alessandria and Parma * Renato Cattaneo (footballer, born 1923), Italian footballer who played for Lucchese, Como and Catania in the 1950s
title: Renato Cattaneo
